CAPITAL
  Show or set your capital sector.

SYNTAX
  capital
  capi

DESCRIPTION
  Displays the location of your current capital sector.  Your
  capital is the reference point for all relative coordinates.
  The capital always has relative coordinates (0,0).

  To move your capital to a new sector, use 'newcap'.

  The capital sector type should remain 'c' (capital designation).
  Your capital provides a slight efficiency and economic bonus.

EXAMPLE
  capital                   show current capital location

SEE ALSO
  newcap  census  map
